---
// Programs.astro
---

<section id="yogyatra" class="w-full bg-[#f9f3e7] flex flex-col md:flex-row min-h-[50vh] lg:min-h-[70vh]">
  
  
  <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 relative h-[40vh] md:h-auto overflow-hidden rounded-b-[2rem] md:rounded-b-none md:rounded-r-[3rem] lg:rounded-r-[4rem] shadow-xl shadow-black/5">
    <img 
      src="/images/v7/yogyatra.jpg" 
      alt="A Journey Beyond The Self" 
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-center"
    />
  </div>

  
  <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left px-8 py-16 md:p-16 lg:p-24 xl:p-32">
    
    
    <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs text-[#8A6345] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-1 font-bold">
      Yogyatra
    </p>

    
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-[#2C241B] italic font-medium leading-tight mb-6 md:mb-8" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">
      A Journey Beyond The Self
    </h2>

    
    <div class="max-w-md text-[#2C241B]/80 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed space-y-3 mb-8" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">
      <p>An invitation to pause… to breathe… to simply be.</p>
      <p>Guided by ancient wisdom, awaken the silence within.</p>
      <p>What you seek has always been within you.</p>
    </div>

    
    <a href="/programs" class="inline-block px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-[#8A6345] text-white font-bold text-[10px] md:text-xs tracking-widest uppercase hover:bg-[#735137] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 shadow-md">
      Discover the Path
    </a>

  </div>

</section>